==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forktail
<hw>Fork"tail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>One of several Asiatic and East Indian passerine
birds, belonging to <gen>Enucurus</gen>, and allied genera. The tail is
deeply forked.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A salmon in its fourth year's
growth.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fork-tailed</ent>⟦br⟧
